  "notes": "Model weights are downloaded from Hugging Face on first use and are not included in this bundle. Word-alignment transcript identity was validated against frozen ASR output, so ASR WER is unchanged by the runtime migration. Packed Torch and sequence ONNX produced identical retained VAD timestamps and downstream transcripts; most VAD compute savings overlap GPU ASR in large folder runs. The exact Transformers 5.13.0 pin protects internal Cohere projection and attention-mask optimizations from unvalidated patch-release changes."
